Package: dragDBI
Type: Package
Title: Calculation of Dragonfly Biotic Index for Odonata communities
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2024-11-30
Author: Prieložná V.(<https://orcid.org/0009-0008-7612-7020>), Pyszko P. (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3743-7201>), Šigutová H. (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1134-248X>), Bílková E.(<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8967-5079>), Dolný A. (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6245-8442>)
Maintainer: Veronika Prieložná <verca.prielozna@gmail.com>
Description: The ‘dragDBI’ package calculates a set of DBI values for odonate communities based on species-level identification. Score types that can be calculated include sum DBI, mean DBI, DBI potential, real DBI potential, and permutational DBI potential. The DBI values can be calculated for the South African Dataset, or a user-uploaded checklist with DBI values. Additionally, the package now includes DBI values for Austria, Switzerland, Czechia, Germany, Poland, Slovakia, and Slovenia based on Bílková et al. (submitted). Definitions of DBI score types are provided in Šigutová et al., 2024.
